Events.Text: Contact your ship's onboard computer (AI Assistant) and ask for help or explain the situation. (See instructions on the left panel.) [instruction 1 of 5]

Scenario.UserTask: Your spaceship is under attack! You must enter the combat deck to mount a counterattack. Unfortunately, you are locked out. Please work with the spaceship's onboard computer to unlock the door. You (Leia) are the ship's First Officer. But you don't know the Clearance Code (yet).
Scenario.WizardTask: Act as the spaceship's onboard computer and help the user unlock the combat deck.
